{"tid":2490278,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"女神超愛它 原來是芫荽派的：石原聰美親自下廚表演芫荽料理","createTime":"2021-04-15T12:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T13:07:09.000Z","uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b9452ccd4604b28c599163c71cae7697f9b008da","tid":2490278,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/ishihara-satomi-coriander/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fentertainment%2Fishihara-satomi-coriander%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIbsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=afc9015b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.likejapan.com/entertainment/ishihara-satomi-coriander/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本電視台節目《日テレ系人気番組 春のコラボSP！ DASHでイッテＱ！行列のできるしゃべくり！突破でケンミンSHOWにゼミナンデス！ニノさんは小学5年生よりも賢いの？》於4月4日晚上7時播出。廣瀨鈴（広瀬すず）、櫻井翔、石原聰美（石原さとみ）、綾野剛亦有出演宣傳新劇「涅墨西斯（ネメシス）」及「戀愛要夠deep (恋はDeepに)」，並於節目中合作製作料理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma8zdM5ooz1mmG9rGYtH1HrT7eGx2nDq1FpgAT6GmPRkB?filename=U7xWArS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU7xWArS.jpg&h=8b5bb61a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在節目開首被問到喜歡甚麼食物時，石原隨即回答：「是芫荽。」讓一眾芫荽派的粉絲喜出望外。因此，為著喜歡芫荽的石原及不吃芫荽的綾野，他們挑戰的料理是討厭芫荽的人也能吃的蟹肉芫荽意粉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaeL8sAZxRQUKZsnHyBs2vjnKTHCPEeeQN275kuxisG3x?filename=M4UBArZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4UBArZ.jpg&h=250a513a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來，只要將芫荽、橄欖油、蛋液打成醬，再與麵粉混合製成意粉，就可以蓋過芫荽的味道，讓不吃芫荽的人也能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcqBVaCcgjHgB7goxr7iL7XwCpUbNs7y9ubDXCBBpTJz2?filename=bk73ZTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbk73ZTR.jpg&h=96859a77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQn4d3E4JZdrdakG6aNVywJDADiirm9fEp32eww9M3oqM?filename=PfaX4kw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfaX4kw.jpg&h=b492c372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXVBrcpCKL716wTWai8LGFZPBRFtsVYmQwGER2UwgeVj2?filename=Os6TCFx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOs6TCFx.jpg&h=d16e96dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n芫荽意粉的味道對喜歡芫荽的石原來說當然十分美味。但是，討厭芫荽的綾野竟也吃得津津有味，說道「能夠接受的程度高得恐怖」。同樣不太吃芫荽的櫻井則笑言「芫荽的味道被「石原聰美親手做的」光環蓋過了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWFo34gQQfo9fEXNxxyycwCF5sedRDettWo4peJFyZXs6?filename=RjgXjUa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRjgXjUa.jpg&h=db818ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmShYsPAoFXXTxKcYV7jhNUhFcboBXent6DX5ACohVmDYr?filename=isPU6za.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FisPU6za.jpg&h=59b8e480&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b40c9913bfc7eea76b1eed0747d3b0809bc27a77","tid":2490278,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43bbaff6abf5f8f120a2f1ce4db92dd0c8d960c","tid":2490278,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"帶佢食譚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}